January 18, 2023

Airbnb Analysis: London, United Kingdom

  • Data Analytics Immersive Program
  • General Assembly, Bahrain
  • Team: Masooma Alghawas, Eman Mohamed, Jubran AlTaitoon, Budoor Sulaiman & Saleh Alfardan
  • Tools:
    • Analysis: Excel
    • Presentation: PowerPoint

This project aims to provide actionable insights for investors seeking to capitalize on the London Airbnb market. Through a comprehensive analysis of Airbnb listing data, we will:

  1. Identify key neighborhood trends based on listing volume, average ratings, and property types.
  2. Estimate average revenue potential for different property configurations within each neighborhood.
  3. Deliver data-driven recommendations for optimal property investments, maximizing return on investment in London's dynamic short-term rental landscape.

Data Source: Inside Airbnb
